noticeDescription: Take Notice that the Council of the City of Toronto has passed By-law No. 75-2018 to designate the property at 69 Long Branch Avenue (St. Agnes’ Church) and 24 Marina Avenue (Rectory of St. Agnes’ Church) as being of cultural heritage value or interest.
